    <br><br>
Sometimes, the changes happen closer to home. Your spouse misplaces the car keys, then forgets names and appointments. At first, it seems like stress or aging, until the truth becomes harder to ignore. Without realizing it, you shift from sharing responsibilities to carrying them.
    <br><br>
In the beginning, it just feels like helping. But somewhere along the way, you’ve become something more — a <a  style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;margin:0 !important;padding:0 !important;line-height:100% !important;mso-line-height-rule:exactly !important;" href="https://click.pulse.celebrations.com/?qs=c6cef39bff559a9b3f6e680860a0850e938b338b2c1b74cd06e0d7297521c868a04b80188833ac24ff05235be133f595fd1059bb83066cbff313e10bf63ec4a0">caregiver</a>.
    <br><br>
Without the tireless and often unseen work of caregivers, our healthcare system would struggle to function. Family members and friends <a  style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;margin:0 !important;padding:0 !important;line-height:100% !important;mso-line-height-rule:exactly !important;" href="https://click.pulse.celebrations.com/?qs=c6cef39bff559a9baec1d84a20d94c73f43e5063a8e021979c268966f976382f529d8a2486239fd55d3632e8b95154b8d8c2fcaf6a30d26a48e0cf11603f74aa">are the backbone</a> of long-term care in this country, filling in the spaces that hospitals and professionals can’t reach.
    <br><br>
That’s why this month — <a  style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;margin:0 !important;padding:0 !important;line-height:100% !important;mso-line-height-rule:exactly !important;" href="https://click.pulse.celebrations.com/?qs=c6cef39bff559a9b354e8ef2e77379ed85b62219efbae777a77791bf3b09952417186c50a0727e1579dc6c53cddae2b7922410076e99b5482c4b00bb6a8d9675">National Family Caregivers Month</a> — is so important. It’s a moment to recognize and thank the millions of people who’ve stepped up to this role. They’re spouses, children, neighbors, and friends who simply saw a need and decided to show up.




